# Security Policy

## Reporting a vulnerability

Please report security vulnerabilities **privately** via
[GitHub Security Advisories](https://github.com/{{ repo_owner }}/{{ project_slug }}/security/advisories/new)
— do not open a public issue. If you can't use that, email <{{ author_email }}>.

We'll acknowledge your report as quickly as we can and keep you posted on the fix.
